title: 长城均衡成长混合A净值上涨3.17%|收益_新浪财经_新浪网
text:
长城均衡成长混合型证券投资基金（简称：长城均衡成长混合A，代码019367）公布4月23日最新净值，上涨3.17%。
长城均衡成长混合A成立于2023年12月25日，业绩比较基准为 收益率×70%+中证港股通综合指数收益率(人民币)×10%+中债综合财富指数收益率×20%。该基金成立以来收益13.73%，今年以来收益13.02%，近一月收益-6.34%，近一年收益10.57%。近一年，该基金排名同类2533/7823。
基金经理为廖瀚博。廖瀚博自2023年11月20日管理（或拟管理）该基金，任职期内收益13.73%。

author: Oleksiy Lutykov
title: War in Ukraine - Nayev congratulated the military on New Year holidays - video
text: "We will liberate and win!" Nayev congratulated the military on New Year holidays. Video The Commander of the Joint Forces of the Armed Forces of Ukraine Serhiy Nayev addressed the servicemen on the occasion of the New Year. The lieutenant general noted that the past year was not easy, but Ukraine has survived and continues to move forward. He also assured that the Ukrainian army will definitely liberate the occupied territories and end this war with a victory over Russia. Nayev posted his New Year's address on [Telegram.](https://t.me/SerhiyNaiev/172) According to him, in 2023, Ukrainian defenders did a lot to bring the victory over the enemy closer. He emphasized the effectiveness of mobile fire groups, which were created in a short time, equipped with weapons and trained to hit air targets. In addition, Nayev noted that in 2023, long-term fortifications were created in dangerous areas of the border. Also, tens of kilometers of minefields and mined rubble were installed, and hundreds of thousands of meters of trenches and anti-tank ditches were dug. "Contrary to all the skeptics' predictions, Ukraine has not fallen, but is stubbornly defending its historical right to a full-fledged free existence in the civilized world. We will definitely liberate the occupied territories and end this terrible war with victory," Nayev said. As a reminder, Nayev said that Ukrainian soldiers from combat units in the Northern Operational Zone [received items necessary for their combat work](https://war.obozrevatel.com/ukr/vognevi-grupi-ppo-otrimali-onovlennya-yake-dopomozhe-krasche-polyuvati-na-shahedi-vnochi.htm), as well as gifts that keep people's hearts warm. Earlier, Serhiy Nayev showed how Ukrainian defenders near the border with Belarus are practicing their readiness to repel the enemy. He noted that the situation is calm now, but it [can change](https://war.obozrevatel.com/ukr/ne-privid-rozslablyatisya-gotovnist-ukrainskih-voiniv-zustriti-voroga-na-pivnochi-pokazali-na-video.htm) at any time. Only verified information is available on our Telegram channel [OBOZ.UA](https://t.me/uaobozrevatel) and [Viber](https://invite.viber.com/?g2=AQA7vCW3MX33iE9EYhmE3GhB43vyI%2B%2BnsqzemGPFrFGfl8TEL3d6MiPUriT1T%2FJF). title: Trabajaba 108 horas a la semana y dormía en una caseta prefabricada
text:

Agentes de la Guardia Civil de Palencia han investigado a una empresa por un supuesto delito contra los derechos de los trabajadores por tener contratada a una persona por 20 horas semanales y realizar 108 horas. Desde que dieran comienzo las obras de la línea de Alta Velocidad entre Palencia y Santander, la Guardia Civil asegura que ha mantenido una vigilancia constante en la zona, no solo para prevenir posibles robos, sino también para tener un control de las empresas y trabajadores.
Con motivo de una visita a una de esas empresas, se comprobó que un trabajador que realizaba funciones de control de acceso y vigilancia, dormía en una caseta prefabricada, a la que sus compañeros de empresa le habían instalado un aparato de aire acondicionado para que no pasara frío y facilitado un baño portátil químico.
Estos hechos se pusieron en conocimiento de la Inspección Provincial de Trabajo y Seguridad Social de Palencia, que pocos días después realizaron una inspección junto a la Guardia Civil, constatando nuevamente las condiciones en las que se encontraba este trabajador.
Según el contrato, el trabajador tendría que realizar «otras actividades de limpieza» durante 20 horas a la semana, aunque realmente realizaba funciones de control de acceso y vigilancia durante 108 horas semanales.
Las diligencias instruidas han quedado a disposición del Juzgado de Instrucción número 1 de Palencia, habiéndose formulado por parte de la Inspección Provincial de Trabajo y Seguridad Social de Palencia un expediente sancionador por infracción muy grave de normas laborales.

author: @AFP
title: South Korean activists send propaganda balloons to N Korea
text:
By AFP June 07, 2024 A balloon believed to have been sent by North Korea, carrying various objects including what appeared to be trash and excrement, is seen over a rice field at Cheorwon on May 29, 2024. — Reuters SEOUL: South Korean activists said on Thursday they had sent 10 balloons loaded with anti-Kim Jong Un leaflets and K-pop music into North Korea, in response to hundreds of trash-carrying balloons from Pyongyang.
North Korea has said its recent balloon blitz -- lugging bags of garbage such as cigarette butts and plastic waste -- was retaliation for previous missives sent by the activists.
Pyongyang called off its campaign on Sunday, but has warned it would restart if more balloons came north.
Past propaganda tit-for-tats have had real-world consequences for inter-Korean relations. South Korea has called the latest provocation from its nuclear-armed neighbour “irrational” and “low-class” but, unlike the North´s spate of recent ballistic missile launches, the trash campaign does not violate UN sanctions on Kim´s isolated government.
The defector group Fighters for Free North Korea announced on Thursday they had launched 10 balloons northward carrying 200,000 leaflets and 5,000 USB flash drives containing Korean pop music and TV shows, as well as thousands of one-dollar bills. A photograph released by the group showed an activist holding up a large poster with photographs of the North´s leader Kim Jong Un and his sister and chief government spokeswoman Kim Yo Jong.
